flowchart TD
    A[Preflight Check] --> B[Survey]
    B --> C[Detection + Geo Tag]
    C --> D[Target Prioritization]
    D --> E[Approach]
    E --> F[Align]
    F --> G[Safe Intervention]
    G --> H[Verify]
    H --> I{More Targets?}
    I -- Yes --> E
    I -- No --> J[Complete + Report]

    A -. fail .-> X[Abort + RTL]
    E -. human detected .-> X
    F -. wind/battery fail .-> X
    G -. guard fail .-> X
